        -         layout of the nlp unknown xu for trapeze discretization 
        -         additional state variable x_{n+1}(t) for the objective (Lagrange to Mayer formulation)
        -         [x_1(t_0), ... , x_{n+1}(t_0),
        -         ... , 
        -         x_{1}(t_N), ... , x_{n+1}(t_N),
        -         u_1(t_0), ... , u_m(t_0), 
